issue.title: Gazebo plugin doesn't build on OS X Mavericks

content.raw:
@\_jrivero_ has been running into some protobuf issues recently.

I'm going to ask for a few things to help with debugging:

* verbose make log, this should show the compiler and linker commands
~~~
make VERBOSE=1
~~~

* list of protobuf libraries in /usr/local/lib
~~~
$ ls -l /usr/local/lib/libproto*
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  51 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-c.0.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf-c/0.15/lib/libprotobuf-c.0.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  45 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-c.a -> ../Cellar/protobuf-c/0.15/lib/libprotobuf-c.a
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  49 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-c.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf-c/0.15/lib/libprotobuf-c.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  53 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.8.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf-lite.8.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  47 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.a -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf-lite.a
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  51 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  48 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf.8.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf.8.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  42 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf.a -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf.a
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  46 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotobuf.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  46 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotoc.8.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotoc.8.dylib
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  40 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotoc.a -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotoc.a
lrwxr-xr-x  1 scpeters  admin  44 Jul  9  2013 /usr/local/lib/libprotoc.dylib -> ../Cellar/protobuf/2.5.0/lib/libprotoc.dylib
~~~

* Check file info for libprotobuf-lite.dylib
~~~
$ file /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib 
/usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib: Mach-O 64-bit dynamically linked shared library x86_64
~~~

* Check which c++ library is linked with libprotobuf-lite.dylib
~~~
$ otool -L /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib | grep c++
	/usr/lib/libstdc++.6.dylib (compatibility version 7.0.0, current version 56.0.0)
~~~

* Search for missing symbol in libprotobuf-lite.dylib
~~~
$ nm /usr/local/lib/libprotobuf-lite.dylib  | grep ParseFromString
000000000000a17a T __ZN6google8protobuf11MessageLite15ParseFromStringERKSs
~~~

Oh, cmake.
